---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="後悔しない看護師転職｜ナース専科×レバウェル看護で理想の職場探し"
  description="納得のいく職場選びを。業界最大手の「ナース専科」と職場のリアルがわかる「レバウェル看護」を徹底比較。あなたにぴったりの正社員・パート求人をプロが厳選紹介。"
  bodyClass="pb-24 md:pb-0"
>
  <header
    class="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm absolute md:fixed w-full z-50 top-0 left-0 h-14 md:h-16 flex items-center justify-between px-4 md:px-8 border-b border-sky-100 transition-all duration-300"
  >
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:gap-4">
      <div class="inline-block select-none">
        <a href="/" class="block hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
          <img
            src="/assets/images/yakusupo_logo.svg"
            alt="看護師Support.com"
            class="h-6 md:h-8 w-auto"
          />
        </a>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-[10px] md:text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded flex items-center whitespace-nowrap"
      >
        <i class="fas fa-bell text-slate-400 mr-1.5 text-[10px]"></i>
        <span id="header-date-text">2026年1月更新</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a
      href="#register"
      class="hidden md:inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[var(--color-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--color-primary-hover)] text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 shadow-md hover:shadow-[var(--color-primary)]/30 text-sm shiny-btn"
    >
      <i class="fas fa-search"></i>好条件の求人を探す（無料）
    </a>
  </header>

  <section
    class="pt-14 md:pt-16 pb-6 md:pb-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-sky-50 via-white to-white relative overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div class="relative z-20">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 py-0.5 border-b border-gray-100">
        <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-2 text-[10px] text-gray-400">
          <span class="border border-gray-300 px-1 rounded-[2px] bg-white text-gray-400 font-medium scale-90">PR</span>
          <span>本ページはプロモーションが含まれています</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10 animate-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out">
      <div class="-mx-4 md:mx-0 relative mb-5 overflow-hidden shadow-soft">
        <a href="#register">
          <picture>
            <source media="(min-width: 768px)" srcset="/assets/images/main.webp" type="image/webp" />
            <source media="(min-width: 768px)" srcset="/assets/images/main.png" />
            <source srcset="/assets/images/main_sp.webp" type="image/webp" />
            <img
              src="/assets/images/main_sp.png"
              alt="笑顔で働く看護師"
              class="w-full h-auto align-middle object-cover"
              width="375"
              height="500"
              fetchpriority="high"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </picture>
        </a>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-slate-600 mt-6 mb-0 md:mb-8 leading-snug px-4">
        <span class="font-bold text-xl md:text-xl">1月は「非公開求人のゴールデンタイム」！</span><br class="md:hidden" />
        納得のいく転職を叶える看護師の正解は
        <span class="text-sky-500 font-bold decoration-sky-500/30 decoration-4">“プロの活用”</span>でした
      </h1>

      <div class="hidden md:inline-flex flex-col items-center gap-2">

        <a
          href="#register"
          class="hidden md:inline-flex shiny-btn group items-center justify-center w-full md:w-auto min-w-[340px] bg-[var(--color-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--color-primary-hover)] text-white text-xl font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-[var(--color-primary)]/30 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          自分にぴったりの求人を紹介してもらう
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-right ml-3 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition"></i>
        </a>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2 text-center">
          ※登録後も無理な転職の勧誘は一切ありません。いつでも退会可能です。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

<section class="bg-white py-8 md:py-14 px-0 md:px-4">
  <div class="w-full md:max-w-5xl mx-auto animate-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out">
    
    <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-8 px-4">
      <h2 class="text-center text-xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">
        私にはどっちが合う？<br />
        <span class="text-sky-600">2大エージェント</span>徹底比較
      </h2>
      <img 
        src="/assets/images/au-bear.png" 
        alt="案内するナースクマ" 
        class="w-12 md:w-20 h-auto object-contain"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="relative w-full">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse text-center table-fixed border-y border-slate-100 md:rounded-xl md:overflow-hidden md:shadow-lg md:border">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <th class="w-[20%] bg-slate-50 py-4 px-1 border-b border-slate-200 text-slate-700 font-bold text-xs md:text-sm align-middle">
              比較項目
            </th>
            <th class="w-[40%] py-4 px-1 border-b-2 border-[var(--color-secondary)] relative border-t-4 md:border-t-8 border-[var(--color-secondary)] border-l border-slate-100">
              <div class="text-[var(--color-secondary)] text-[9px] md:text-xs font-bold mb-2 tracking-tighter uppercase">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt mr-0.5"></i>職場のリアル
              </div>
              <div class="h-8 md:h-12 flex items-center justify-center">
                <img src="/assets/images/logo_reverage.svg" alt="レバウェル看護" class="max-h-full w-auto object-contain" />
              </div>
            </th>
            <th class="w-[40%] py-4 px-1 border-b-2 border-sky-500 relative border-t-4 md:border-t-8 border-sky-500 border-l border-slate-100">
              <div class="text-sky-500 text-[9px] md:text-xs font-bold mb-2 tracking-tighter uppercase">
                <i class="fas fa-crown mr-0.5"></i>求人数・安心感
              </div>
              <div class="h-8 md:h-12 flex items-center justify-center">
                <img src="/assets/images/logo_nursesenka.webp" alt="ナース専科" class="max-h-full w-auto object-contain" />
              </div>
            </th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        
        <tbody class="bg-white divide-y divide-slate-100">
          <tr>
            <td class="bg-slate-50 font-bold text-slate-700 text-xs md:text-sm align-middle">最大の強み</td>
            <td class="py-5 px-1 border-l border-slate-100">
              <span class="text-[var(--color-secondary)] font-bold text-xs md:text-lg block mb-1">職場の内情報</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] md:text-sm text-slate-500 block leading-tight">働いたナースの生の声</span>
            </td>
            <td class="py-5 px-1 border-l border-slate-100">
              <span class="text-sky-600 font-bold text-xs md:text-lg block mb-1">国内最大級の求人数</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] md:text-sm text-slate-500 block leading-tight">求人数20万件以上（※2024/3月時点）</span>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
          <tr>
            <td class="bg-slate-50 font-bold text-slate-700 text-xs md:text-sm align-middle">サポート</td>
            <td class="py-5 px-1 border-l border-slate-100">
              <span class="text-slate-800 font-bold text-xs md:text-lg block mb-1">徹底ヒアリング</span>
              <p class="text-[10px] md:text-sm text-slate-500 leading-tight">ミスマッチを最小化</p>
            </td>
            <td class="py-5 px-1 border-l border-slate-100">
              <span class="text-slate-800 font-bold text-xs md:text-lg block mb-1">交渉力に定評</span>
              <p class="text-[10px] md:text-sm text-slate-500 leading-tight">過去の成約事例が豊富 面接対策・条件交渉もお任せ</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
          <tr>
            <td class="bg-slate-50 font-bold text-slate-700 text-xs md:text-sm align-middle">こんな人に</td>
            <td class="py-5 px-1 border-l border-slate-100">
              <div class="inline-block bg-[var(--color-secondary)] text-white text-[9px] md:text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-bold mb-1.5">納得感重視</div>
              <p class="text-[10px] md:text-sm text-slate-500 leading-tight">現場の雰囲気を<br/>重視したい方</p>
            </td>
            <td class="py-5 px-1 border-l border-slate-100">
              <div class="inline-block bg-sky-500 text-white text-[9px] md:text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-bold mb-1.5">LINEで気軽にやり取り</div>
              <p class="text-[10px] md:text-sm text-slate-500 leading-tight">忙しくて頻繁に電話に出られない人でも<br>安心して利用できる</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
          <tr>
            <td class="bg-slate-50 font-bold text-slate-700 text-xs md:text-sm align-middle">利用料</td>
            <td class="p-2 md:p-5 border-l border-slate-100">
              <a href="/link/levwell" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="block bg-[var(--color-secondary)] hover:bg-[var(--color-secondary-hover)] text-white text-xs md:text-sm font-bold py-3 rounded-lg shadow-md transition-all duration-300 shiny-btn">
                レバウェル看護公式サイトへ（無料）
              </a>
              <p class="text-[8px] md:text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-1.5"></p>
            </td>
            <td class="p-2 md:p-5 border-l border-slate-100">
              <a href="/link/nursesenka" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="block bg-[var(--color-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--color-primary-hover)] text-white text-xs md:text-sm font-bold py-3 rounded-lg shadow-md transition-all duration-300 shiny-btn">
                ナース専科公式サイトへ（無料）
              </a>
              <p class="text-[8px] md:text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-1.5"></p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

  <div class="w-full">
    <section class="w-full bg-sky-50 pt-10 md:pt-16 pb-14 md:pb-20 relative">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 relative z-10 animate-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out">
        <div class="text-center mb-10 md:mb-14">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-slate-900">
            今の職場、こんな<span class="text-sky-500 relative inline-block">悩み</span><br class="md:hidden" />ありませんか？
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 md:gap-10">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-4 -bottom-4 w-full h-full bg-sky-200 rounded-[2rem] -z-10 hidden md:block transform -rotate-2"></div>
            <div class="relative transform -rotate-2">
              <img src="/assets/images/nayami.png" alt="悩む看護師" class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 md:mb-10 text-center md:text-left">
              現場の「我慢」が限界に近い方へ
            </h3>

            <ul class="space-y-8 md:space-y-10">
              <li class="flex items-start group">
                <div class="shrink-0 mr-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock text-sky-500 text-3xl"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 leading-tight">サービス残業・人手不足で体力が持たない</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">「終わるまで帰れない」のが当たり前。自分の時間が削られ、心身ともに疲弊している。</p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="flex items-start group">
                <div class="shrink-0 mr-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-yen-sign text-sky-500 text-3xl"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 leading-tight">業務の責任に対して給与が見合わない</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">命を預かる重責と多忙な日々。それなのに昇給はわずかで、将来に不安を感じている。</p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="flex items-start group">
                <div class="shrink-0 mr-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-users-slash text-sky-500 text-3xl"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 leading-tight">人間関係のストレスで心が休まらない</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">独特な緊張感や派閥争い。看護に集中したいのに、周囲への気遣いだけで疲れてしまう。</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="absolute left-0 right-0 bottom-0 flex justify-center translate-y-[99%] z-20"> <div class="w-0 h-0 border-l-[40px] border-l-transparent border-r-[40px] border-r-transparent border-t-[30px] border-t-sky-50"></div> </div>
    </section>

    <section class="w-full bg-white pt-16 md:pt-20 pb-10 md:pb-16 relative z-0">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 animate-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out">
        <div class="text-center mb-10 md:mb-14">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight">
            <span class="text-sky-600">“エージェント活用”</span>という賢い選択
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 text-sm md:text-base">自分一人で探すより、圧倒的に「理想」に近づけます</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-10 md:gap-10">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative">
            <div class="absolute -right-4 -bottom-4 w-full h-full bg-blue-100 rounded-[2rem] -z-10 hidden md:block transform rotate-2"></div>
            <div class="relative transform rotate-2">
              <img src="/assets/images/after.png" alt="笑顔の看護師" class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-[2rem] shadow-2xl shadow-yellow-100/50" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
            <ul class="space-y-8 md:space-y-10">
              <li class="flex items-start group">
                <div class="shrink-0 mr-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-sky-600 text-3xl"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">高条件な「非公開求人」を優先紹介</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">一般には公開されない年収500万超や土日休み等の優良案件を、登録者限定で紹介。</p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="flex items-start group">
                <div class="shrink-0 mr-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-search-plus text-sky-600 text-3xl"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">職場の「本当の内情」を事前リサーチ</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">離職率、残業の実態、師長さんの人柄など、求人票には載らないリアルを共有。</p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="flex items-start group">
                <div class="shrink-0 mr-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-comments-dollar text-sky-600 text-3xl"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">給与や休日の「条件交渉」を代行</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">自分では言いにくい「もう少し給与を…」という交渉も、プロが代わりに行います。</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="py-10 md:py-16 px-4 bg-sky-50/50 border-sky-200">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto animate-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out">
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-8 md:mb-14">
        「転職して本当によかった」<br />先輩ナースの声
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 pt-10 md:p-8 md:pt-12 rounded-2xl shadow-soft relative mt-6 md:mt-0 border border-sky-100">
          <div class="absolute -top-6 md:-top-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
            <img src="/assets/images/user01.png" alt="User" loading="lazy" class="w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <span class="inline-block bg-sky-100 text-slate-600 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3">29歳・病棟からクリニック</span>
            <span class="inline-block bg-sky-100 text-sky-600 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3">年収アップ・残業なし</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-5 leading-snug">
              「夜勤なし」でも年収維持！<br />
              <span class="text-sky-500">心にゆとりができました</span>
            </h3>
            <div class="bg-sky-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4 text-sm">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs">前職</span>
                <span class="text-slate-400 font-medium line-through">不規則なシフト・過労</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-sky-600 text-xs font-bold">現在</span>
                <span class="text-slate-900 font-bold text-base">日勤のみ・土日祝休み</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-sub-text text-left leading-relaxed">
              以前は毎日ヘトヘトで、家に帰っても何もする気が起きませんでした。エージェントさんに交渉してもらい好条件のクリニックへ転職。今では生活リズムが整い、週末に趣味を楽しむ余裕ができました。月の手取りも5万円増え、貯金もできるように。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="more-reviews" class="hidden md:contents">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 pt-10 md:p-8 md:pt-12 rounded-2xl shadow-soft relative mt-10 md:mt-0 border border-sky-100 animate-fade-in">
            <div class="absolute -top-6 md:-top-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
              <img src="/assets/images/user02.png" alt="User" loading="lazy" class="w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <span class="inline-block bg-sky-100 text-slate-600 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3">35歳・子育て中</span>
              <span class="inline-block bg-sky-100 text-sky-600 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3">時短勤務・理解ある職場</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-5 leading-snug">
                お迎えの焦りから解放！<br />
                <span class="text-sky-500">子育てに理解ある環境</span>へ
              </h3>
              <div class="bg-sky-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4 text-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                  <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs">前職</span>
                  <span class="text-slate-400 font-medium line-through">時短なのに残業あり</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-sky-600 text-xs font-bold">現在</span>
                  <span class="text-slate-900 font-bold text-base">残業ゼロ・理解ある同僚</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-sub-text text-left leading-relaxed">
                子どもが熱を出しても「お互い様だよ」と言ってもらえる職場。保育園のお迎えに間に合わず焦ることもなくなり、子どもとの時間が増えました。プロに相談して本当に正解でした。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 pt-10 md:p-8 md:pt-12 rounded-2xl shadow-soft relative mt-10 md:mt-0 border border-sky-100 animate-fade-in">
            <div class="absolute -top-6 md:-top-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
              <img src="/assets/images/user03.png" alt="User" loading="lazy" class="w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
